headline: 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Boost Your Passive Income in 2025
summary: The stock market has gotten off to a rough start this year, as Wall Street focuses on the possibility of a recession.  One way to weather market volatility is to focus on quality dividend stocks, and this is the perfect time to consider adding some to your portfolio.  Lower share prices have driven up the yields of strong businesses that have been paying regular dividends for decades.
